See `ASSUMPTIONS.md` for full dependency contracts.

## API Contract

Base path: `/v1`
Auth: Bearer JWT (RS256)
Errors: `{"error":{"code":"...","message":"...","fields":{...}}}`
Pagination: cursor-based (`?cursor=...&limit=N`)

